sentences: Nweke Joy Chinenye Serrato (born 23 February 1999), professionally known as Supernovamusician, is a Nigerian singer, songwriter, actress, movie producer, story writer and CEO of Supernova Music Worldwide.
She kicked off her music career by starting her own record label in 2019 and in 2020.
